<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.10">
<l>kariya māmukil paṭalaṅkaḷ kiṭantavai muḻaṅkiṭa kaḷiṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>periya mācuṇam varaiyeṉap peyartaru</l>
<l>piritiyem perumāṉai</l>
<l>varikoḷ vaṇṭaṟai paimpoḻil maṅkaiyar kaliyaṉa tolimālai</l>
<l>ariya viṉṉicai pāṭunal laṭiyavark karuviṉai yaṭaiyāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those good devotees who sing the rare, sweet music</l>
<l rend="indent">of this garland of words</l>
<l>Of Kaliyaṉ of those of Maṅkai, with green groves where striped bees hum,</l>
<l>About our great lord of Piriti where,</l>
<l rend="indent">when large, dark, stationary cloud masses thunder,</l>
<l>Pythons, huge like elephants, are spurred to move like mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent">harsh karma will not reach [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
